snippet.title: Voidtrain - Official Trailer | Publisher Spotlight Showcase 2023 (HypeTrain Digital)
snippet.description:
Take a peek at what’s coming up for Voidtrain, like additional Void creatures and more, in this latest spotlight for the survival crafting FPS game. Voidtrain is available now in Early Access, and its first content update arrives this summer.

#IGN #SoG
